OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784659707
OL,3,CCountdown to Balloon Fiesta begins
OL,4,Cwith sunrise flight
OL,6,FAround 10 hot air balloons took off
OL,7,Ffrom College Green for a sunrise
OL,8,Fascent to kick off preparations for
OL,9,Fthe 48th Bristol International Balloon
OL,10,FFiesta
OL,12,FHot air balloons have filled the skies
OL,13,Fabove Bristol to mark the official
OL,14,Fcountdown to the International Balloon
OL,15,FFiesta.
OL,17,F12 balloons took off from College
OL,18,FGreen and headed towards Ashton Court
OL,19,FEstate, where the free event will take
OL,20,Fplace from Friday 7 August to Sunday
OL,21,F11 August.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
