PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784659707
OL,3,CCountdown to Balloon Fiesta begins
OL,4,Cwith sunrise flight
OL,6,FNow in its 48th year, the popular
OL,7,Fevent celebrates Bristol and its
OL,8,Fheritage links to the world of hot air
OL,9,Fballooning.
OL,11,FThe activity has been part of
OL,12,FBristol's culture for many years, with
OL,13,Fthe first recorded flight in the city
OL,14,Fdating back to the 18th century.
OL,16,FCommercial hot air balloon pilot Steve
OL,17,FWithers flew an Albert Goodman balloon
OL,18,Fduring the ascent and praised the
OL,19,F"perfect" conditions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784659707
OL,3,CCountdown to Balloon Fiesta begins
OL,4,Cwith sunrise flight
OL,6,FHe said: "It's amazing flying around
OL,7,FBristol and the surrounding area.
OL,9,F"Bristol is the capital of ballooning
OL,10,Ffor the UK, and it's world-renowned
OL,11,Ffor the Balloon Fiesta that's been
OL,12,Fgoing for such a long time."
OL,14,FMore than 100 hot air balloons are
OL,15,Fexpected to take part in this year's
OL,16,Fmass ascents, scheduled for early
OL,17,Fmorning and evening each day during
OL,18,Fthe Fiesta - though this is weather
OL,19,Fpermitting.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
