FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784659707
OL,3,CCountdown to Balloon Fiesta begins
OL,4,Cwith sunrise flight
OL,6,FBalloons of all shapes and sizes from
OL,7,Facross the UK, Belgium, Switzerland,
OL,8,Fthe Netherlands, Germany, Mexico and
OL,9,Fthe United States will take part in
OL,10,Fthe spectacle.
OL,12,FThe Bristol International Balloon
OL,13,FFiesta has announced this year's line-
OL,14,Fup will include a range of "beloved
OL,15,Fclassics," "recent favourites," and
OL,16,F"new additions".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
