FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784659707
OL,3,CCountdown to Balloon Fiesta begins
OL,4,Cwith sunrise flight
OL,6,FSpecial shape balloons will be present
OL,7,Fat the event, including Slick the
OL,8,FDragon, Wallace & Gromit's Moon
OL,9,FRocket, Astro the Alien, Daisy the
OL,10,FCow, and Slither the Snake.
OL,12,FHistoric special shape balloons, which
OL,13,Fwill tether in the main area include
OL,14,FBBC Globe, Thomas the Tank Engine,
OL,15,FOrdnance Survey Map, Piggy Bank, and
OL,16,Fthe Orient Express.
OL,18,FIn the evenings, dozens of tethered
OL,19,Fballoons will light up in sync to a
OL,20,Fspecial musical soundtrack for the
OL,21,Ffiesta's popular "night glows".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
